CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 1, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "'Way Up There! - They're Aniketos, at Clairton swimming pool.  On ladder: Lois Weaver, Rose Marie Lawrence, Frank Enty.  On platform: Don Mattheus [Matheus], Jimmy Bertha, Mozelle Thompson.  On slide: William Battles and Eugenia Scott. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Lois Weaver Watson and Rosemarie Lawrence climbing ladder, Frank Entry seated, Don Matheus, Jimmy Bertha, Mozelle Thompson standing, and William Battles and Eugenia Scott sliding down ladder, at swimming pool in Clairton
